{"tid":686990,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(喺一個黑暗密室入面 放一盞燈","createTime":"2018-06-01T20:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T08:14:21.000Z","uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"df7a761e4ba1b2e094a7f1ddab8509177dfd770f","tid":686990,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T20:05:35.000Z","msg":"假設盞燈係一個球體<br />\n可以喺四面八方射出光線 (假設1:光線係perfect sine curve;假設2:因為個密室好細 而且光線夠強 光線隨travel distance 嘅減弱係微乎其微)<br />\n當光線碰到牆壁 就會反射(假設反射嘅物質對光線減弱嘅影響係微乎其微)<br />\n咁自然地 喺密室入面某啲點 會有多過一條光線相遇<br />\n雖然我地唔知到喺某一點上每條光線之間嘅phase difference係點<br />\n但假設有啲係0, 有啲係pi<br />\n換句話講 有啲係constructive interference, 有啲係destructive interference<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪喺一間有光嘅房間入面嘅某一啲特別嘅點係完全黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可能用儀器觀察到呢一啲點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee65b82d2fb247890c7703ef8d3c338cb9b3086","tid":686990,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T20:20:56.000Z","msg":"點解「喺密室入面某啲點 會有多過一條光線相遇」<br />\n同埋sine curve係想講d光係sine wave?<br />\n係咪monochrome?"},{"pid":"d414f0b061c598fca76f85138db0d233a35b2717","tid":686990,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T20:24:20.000Z","msg":"唔明"},{"pid":"09fd60a42ff31ffb0e132c5f3499034d1b87d99d","tid":686990,"uid":65858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T20:39:53.000Z","msg":"光線疊光線唔會destrutive 除非你玩slit experiment或者polarization<br />\n<br />\n利申 鳩up"},{"pid":"6e5256c8a703a1b9f22dfb80e5a7a6e096f7cfef","tid":686990,"uid":67645,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T03:21:35.000Z","msg":"試下轉做2d去諗<br />\n<br />\nlight sources放左係個盒入面<br />\n個盒嘅4面都識反射...(條件如題<br />\n<br />\n當個source開始運作<br />\n光以circle wave嘅樣放射出去<br />\n咁嗰個source嘅wave就會同reflected wave interfere<br />\n<br />\n樓主個picture係咪咁？"},{"pid":"10e945c5873063a2b9adf179158120ef262e58bd","tid":686990,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ee65b82d2fb247890c7703ef8d3c338cb9b3086","tid":686990,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T20:20:56.000Z","msg":"點解「喺密室入面某啲點 會有多過一條光線相遇」<br />\n同埋sine curve係想講d光係sine wave?<br />\n係咪monochrome?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:23:10.000Z","msg":"可以諗做multipath <br />\n係 無錯 我打錯字"},{"pid":"a5c75f446e1f168907cf2dfa53241cd85a116a3c","tid":686990,"uid":137768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e5256c8a703a1b9f22dfb80e5a7a6e096f7cfef","tid":686990,"uid":67645,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T03:21:35.000Z","msg":"試下轉做2d去諗<br />\n<br />\nlight sources放左係個盒入面<br />\n個盒嘅4面都識反射...(條件如題<br />\n<br />\n當個source開始運作<br />\n光以circle wave嘅樣放射出去<br />\n咁嗰個source嘅wave就會同reflected wave interfere<br />\n<br />\n樓主個picture係咪咁？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:24:27.000Z","msg":"係 無錯 想講multipath effect"},{"pid":"8f65cd701a3b1f8ba9d63af059fb944cf5470cd8","tid":686990,"uid":107505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:53:09.000Z","msg":"要睇下做唔做到standing wave(?)"},{"pid":"11c4ab313e9d196431a0d8012302aa7fa45fe8e9","tid":686990,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f65cd701a3b1f8ba9d63af059fb944cf5470cd8","tid":686990,"uid":107505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T04:53:09.000Z","msg":"要睇下做唔做到standing wave(?)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:03:16.000Z","msg":"唔一定係opposite direction"},{"pid":"3e7bad3e1dbf2d6f36d228aa34c442d2bd5a0f69","tid":686990,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ee65b82d2fb247890c7703ef8d3c338cb9b3086","tid":686990,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T20:20:56.000Z","msg":"點解「喺密室入面某啲點 會有多過一條光線相遇」<br />\n同埋sine curve係想講d光係sine wave?<br />\n係咪monochrome?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"漏左覆 係monochrome 或者咁講 當frequency/amplitude against frequency 係uniform<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e681d18238a08ade9d6e09aa516d4f421b85a3be","tid":686990,"uid":65858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09fd60a42ff31ffb0e132c5f3499034d1b87d99d","tid":686990,"uid":65858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T20:39:53.000Z","msg":"光線疊光線唔會destrutive 除非你玩slit experiment或者polarization<br />\n<br />\n利申 鳩up"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:15:38.000Z","msg":"點解無視左我個回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且又唔係講緊data transmit 關multipath effect咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c63d44a041bf310d202f817ce082c945bd4356d","tid":686990,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e681d18238a08ade9d6e09aa516d4f421b85a3be","tid":686990,"uid":65858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09fd60a42ff31ffb0e132c5f3499034d1b87d99d","tid":686990,"uid":65858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T20:39:53.000Z","msg":"光線疊光線唔會destrutive 除非你玩slit experiment或者polarization<br />\n<br />\n利申 鳩up"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:15:38.000Z","msg":"點解無視左我個回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且又唔係講緊data transmit 關multipath effect咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T05:37:33.000Z","msg":"sorry 啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為一開始唔係幾知點覆你<br />\nMultipath(形容radio signals)係比喻黎 因為而家喺間房入面啲material可以反射光線"},{"pid":"afec855316998223fc29f94bb40e9deec9909014","tid":686990,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T08:30:59.000Z","msg":"應該搵啲識寫program嘅巴打模擬下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n數學上我諗應該計下intensity分佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 2樣都唔識"},{"pid":"aea9927dffa6350460931523085a291e45f54531","tid":686990,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:01:35.000Z","msg":"我嘗試翻譯一下<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>假設盞燈係一個球體<br />\n可以喺四面八方射出光線 (假設1:光線係perfect sine curve;假設2:因為個密室好細 而且光線夠強 光線隨travel distance 嘅減弱係微乎其微)</blockquote><br />\n假設有一個球對稱單色相干光源 介質所導致既衰減可忽略<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>當光線碰到牆壁 就會反射(假設反射嘅物質對光線減弱嘅影響係微乎其微)</blockquote><br />\n反射既衰減可忽略 同時忽略反射對相干性既影響<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>咁自然地 喺密室入面某啲點 會有多過一條光線相遇<br />\n雖然我地唔知到喺某一點上每條光線之間嘅phase difference係點<br />\n但假設有啲係0, 有啲係pi<br />\n換句話講 有啲係constructive interference, 有啲係destructive interference<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪喺一間有光嘅房間入面嘅某一啲特別嘅點係完全黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可能用儀器觀察到呢一啲點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n是否存在一點 使得其干涉振幅為零"},{"pid":"f03b6b9d1220c25bbd029eb7944273f4b7fa7839","tid":686990,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:06:21.000Z","msg":"咁其實就有個位要釐清先可以開始去解答呢條問題<br />\n我地到底討論緊咩optics<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Geometrical optics定wave optics定electromagnetism定QED<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信大家都同意唔係Geometrical 亦唔係QED<br />\n但係係討論緊wave optics定electromagnetism<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a75b8c63df045d077bc20f6fd1741674fc2ce6","tid":686990,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f03b6b9d1220c25bbd029eb7944273f4b7fa7839","tid":686990,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":