"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4c2266d511db7a1c747234ebab9fe8abb50128e","tid":686990,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5a75b8c63df045d077bc20f6fd1741674fc2ce6","tid":686990,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f03b6b9d1220c25bbd029eb7944273f4b7fa7839","tid":686990,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:06:21.000Z","msg":"咁其實就有個位要釐清先可以開始去解答呢條問題<br />\n我地到底討論緊咩optics<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Geometrical optics定wave optics定electromagnetism定QED<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我相信大家都同意唔係Geometrical 亦唔係QED<br />\n但係係討論緊wave optics定electromagnetism<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:16:38.000Z","msg":"巴打可唔可以講解一下兩者，wave optics and electromagnetism,嘅討論方向有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T11:35:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physical_optics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FPhysical_optics&d=F49045if5U1yo1pgcUX29S7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=ba2bdc70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physical_optics</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T16:16:37.000Z","msg":"唔知有無get錯<br />\n<br />\nGeometric optics: 有reflection 有refraction 無wave effects e.g. interference <br />\n(所以唔係我假設嘅情境入面 因為有interference)<br />\n<br />\nPhysical optics: 會考慮wave effects (應該係假設情境入面嘅野都適用)<br />\n<br />\nElectromagnetism: 再broad啲 考慮所有EM waves 但好似同並無考慮到咁闊<br />\n<br />\n我講得唔清楚嘅話可以再問"},{"pid":"5c28018c4cc025392de3d077b3b3ce9125242e3b","tid":686990,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T19:08:33.000Z","msg":"想問問個sine wave有冇厚度?"},{"pid":"b8680b5a136fc78baba5babab4e9de8ec5c10042","tid":686990,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c28018c4cc025392de3d077b3b3ce9125242e3b","tid":686990,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T19:08:33.000Z","msg":"想問問個sine wave有冇厚度?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:35:51.000Z","msg":"喺我學過嘅wave model入面 無thickness呢樣野 只有amplitude同time/travel distance兩個dimensions<br />\nChing想指spiral waves? photons?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056f4872b93d0179fef1ddae067169e635ceb4a7","tid":686990,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:59:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問問個sine wave有冇厚度?</blockquote>喺我學過嘅wave model入面 無thickness呢樣野 只有amplitude同time/travel distance兩個dimensions<br />\nChing想指<span style=\"color: red;\">plane waves</span>? photons?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dbc4a6d119eaae83d2c6fe8a3aa78e7c0f91d5","tid":686990,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T05:06:39.000Z","msg":"睇多左少少資料 好似polarization都關事 assume題目係linearly polarized light應該合理啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7447e3e88be36a812721c3e98b45260ed798b3","tid":686990,"uid":67089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T06:46:48.000Z","msg":"你唔係讀屎片就係弱智既，咁撚細既地方點觀察"},{"pid":"228047a2f282c8940b17a41adb96d04003208dd3","tid":686990,"uid":113178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T07:06:19.000Z","msg":"燈唔係coherent source, 整唔到stable interference pattern，所以唔會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b759357339ac66e8fb691a3fed2e421354979fe","tid":686990,"uid":69994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"228047a2f282c8940b17a41adb96d04003208dd3","tid":686990,"uid":113178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T07:06:19.000Z","msg":"燈唔係coherent source, 整唔到stable interference pattern，所以唔會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T07:17:41.000Z","msg":"係囉 , 係牆面個反射係 漫射 diffuse , 就算有某一點呢一刻係 constructive / destructive interference , 0.000000...1 秒之後已經唔係 .<br />\n<br />\n不過有時睇新聞 , 有D實驗駛左億億聲 , 就係為左觀察呢0.000000...1 秒之內發生既事 ."}]}